# AI Engineering Harness

When working in this repository, treat `.harness/` as the project operating system when those files exist.

## Required reads

- `.harness/HARNESS.md`, `TEAM.md`, `WORKFLOW.md`, `GATES.md` when present
- Active goal under `.harness/goals/` when executing a goal
- Root `AGENTS.md` for agent contract

## Behavior

- Plan before coding; verify before claiming done
- Keep scope surgical; do not copy the full harness pack into the product tree
- Use harness workflows (`harness-map` through `harness-remember`) when the project profile selects them

See https://github.com/truongnat/ai-engineering-harness for pack documentation.
